            "text": "Baby, do you understand me now?\nSometimes I feel a little mad",
            "label": "",
            "size": {
              "width": 1920,
              "height": 1080
            },
            "trigger time": [
              0.0
            ]
          },
          {
            "enabled": true,
            "notes": "",
            "text": "But don't you know that no one alive\nCan always be an angel?\nWhen things go wrong I seem to be bad",
            "label": "",
            "size": {
              "width": 1920,
              "height": 1080
            },
            "trigger time": [
